# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:4
translate portuguese act3scene4_594c2912:

    # "In a blink, I'm suddenly back in the Ice Queen's throne room."
    "Num piscar de olhos, de repente estou de volta à sala do trono da Rainha do Gelo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:6
translate portuguese act3scene4_41d6859f:

    # "My friends are still frozen around me, but I feel my body thawing."
    "Os meus amigos continuam congelados à minha volta, mas sinto o meu corpo a descongelar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:9
translate portuguese act3scene4_785bdb9f:

    # "When I can move again, I stumble forward and almost fall."
    "Quando consigo mover-me novamente, tropeço para a frente e quase caio."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:10
translate portuguese act3scene4_9fe7bb42:

    # "But I'm able to stop myself and it seems that the Ice Queen didn't notice."
    "Mas consigo parar-me e parece que a Rainha do Gelo não reparou."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:11
translate portuguese act3scene4_269679eb:

    # "Time to make my move."
    "Está na hora de agir."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:15
translate portuguese act3scene4_f4ddd564:

    # "I rush up and hug her from behind, pulling her close to me."
    "Corro e abraço-a por trás, puxando-a para perto de mim."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:16
translate portuguese act3scene4_6145e44f:

    # sp "WHAT!?"
    sp "O QUÊ!?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:17
translate portuguese act3scene4_d519fcc2:

    # sp "{i}WHAT{/i} are you doing? Unhand me!"
    sp "{i}O QUE{/i} estás a fazer? Larga-me!"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:20
translate portuguese act3scene4_0d90b60a:

    # pc "I'm sorry that you lost Suzy. I'm so sorry that happened to you."
    pc "Lamento que tenhas perdido a Suzy. Lamento imenso que isso te tenha acontecido."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:21
translate portuguese act3scene4_641a9d68:

    # sp "Don't say her name--"
    sp "Não digas o nome dela..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:22
translate portuguese act3scene4_ad5d8a1e:

    # pc "I know your heart is broken."
    pc "Sei que tens o coração partido."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:23
translate portuguese act3scene4_c39f9ad8:

    # pc "That just shows how much love you had."
    pc "Isso só mostra o quanto a amavas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:24
translate portuguese act3scene4_eb5ca914:

    # sp "You don't know--"
    sp "Tu não sabes..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:27
translate portuguese act3scene4_82d048f3:

    # pc "Suzy wants you to know that she loves you so much."
    pc "A Suzy quer que saibas que te ama imenso."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:28
translate portuguese act3scene4_acba1f83:

    # sp "Stop--"
    sp "Pára..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:31
translate portuguese act3scene4_cdd644dd:

    # pc "She wants you to know that she's going to always be with you."
    pc "Ela quer que saibas que vai estar sempre contigo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:32
translate portuguese act3scene4_10d0ad27:

    # sp "How do you--"
    sp "Como é que tu..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:35
translate portuguese act3scene4_978f88d1:

    # pc "And she doesn't like seeing what you've become."
    pc "E ela não gosta de ver no que te tornaste."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:36
translate portuguese act3scene4_8144a68d:

    # pc "She wants you to be warm and loving again, like she remembers you."
    pc "Ela quer que voltes a ser calorosa e amorosa, tal como ela se lembra de ti."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:37
translate portuguese act3scene4_ad07f09a:

    # sp "I'm not--"
    sp "Eu não sou..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:40
translate portuguese act3scene4_38d06822:

    # "She doesn't finish her sentence, instead bursting into tears and crumpling in my arms."
    "Ela não termina a frase, em vez disso, desata a chorar e desaba nos meus braços."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:41
translate portuguese act3scene4_5b98a3b5:

    # pc "I'm sorry, Lisa. I'm sorry she's gone."
    pc "Desculpa, Lisa. Lamento que ela se tenha ido."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:42
translate portuguese act3scene4_d761b7e0:

    # pc "I love you."
    pc "Amo-te."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:45
translate portuguese act3scene4_3689094d:

    # "I hold her for a long time while she cries."
    "Agarro-a por um longo tempo enquanto ela chora."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:46
translate portuguese act3scene4_fcd85bea:

    # "I wonder if she's ever let herself really feel the loss."
    "Pergunto-me se ela alguma vez se permitiu sentir verdadeiramente a perda."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:47
translate portuguese act3scene4_6f05f3c1:

    # "I wonder if she's ever had anybody to hold her like this."
    "Pergunto-me se ela alguma vez teve alguém para a abraçar assim."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:50
translate portuguese act3scene4_49651a35:

    # "After some time, she stops crying and sits up again."
    "Passado algum tempo, ela pára de chorar e senta-se novamente."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:51
translate portuguese act3scene4_77d46c18:

    # sp "Who {i}are{/i} you?"
    sp "Quem {i}és{/i} tu?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:52
translate portuguese act3scene4_22be1576:

    # pc "It's a long story..."
    pc "É uma longa história..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:53
translate portuguese act3scene4_0eb855c9:

    # "So I tell her everything about the other world, about the bracelet, about coming here to see her."
    "Então conto-lhe tudo sobre o outro mundo, sobre a pulseira, sobre ter vindo aqui para a ver."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:56
translate portuguese act3scene4_299824e4:

    # sp "You did so much to find your father."
    sp "Fizeste tanto para encontrar o teu pai."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:57
translate portuguese act3scene4_4aa0965e:

    # pc "Well yeah... I love him."
    pc "Bem, sim... Eu amo-o."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:58
translate portuguese act3scene4_2c93668b:

    # sp "I suppose so. I'd do anything to get Suzy back."
    sp "Suponho que sim. Faria qualquer coisa para ter a Suzy de volta."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:61
translate portuguese act3scene4_f8215d8f:

    # pc "I know, [mom]... but sometimes people can't come back."
    pc "Eu sei, [mom]... mas às vezes as pessoas não podem voltar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:62
translate portuguese act3scene4_2022e63e:

    # pc "We lose people that we love sometimes..."
    pc "Às vezes perdemos pessoas que amamos..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:63
translate portuguese act3scene4_d1689608:

    # pc "...and we have to find a way to deal with that without hurting ourselves or others."
    pc "... e temos de encontrar uma maneira de lidar com isso sem nos magoarmos a nós próprios ou aos outros."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:66
translate portuguese act3scene4_c3dfeaa2:

    # sp "How? How can a person deal with that sort of loss?"
    sp "Como? Como é que uma pessoa lida com esse tipo de perda?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:68
translate portuguese act3scene4_8b7fb492:

    # pc "Well, in my world..."
    pc "Bem, no meu mundo..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:72
translate portuguese act3scene4_22817e0f:

    # pc "... Nora lost what she thought her life was going to be."
    pc "... a Nora perdeu aquilo que pensava que a sua vida iria ser."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:73
translate portuguese act3scene4_a6290b41:

    # pc "The man that was supposed to love her treated her badly and she was forced into this new life."
    pc "O homem que era suposto amá-la tratou-a mal e ela foi forçada a entrar nesta nova vida."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:74
translate portuguese act3scene4_1e07804a:

    # pc "But she dove in and accepted it and is thriving on her own now."
    pc "Mas ela mergulhou de cabeça, aceitou-a e agora está a prosperar por conta própria."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:75
translate portuguese act3scene4_03b53305:

    # pc "She's discovering that there's a lot of love out there if you let yourself be open to it."
    pc "Ela está a descobrir que há muito amor por aí, se nos deixarmos abrir a ele."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:79
translate portuguese act3scene4_ff6ea314:

    # pc "... Reba's father passed away and it put her whole family in a sort of limbo."
    pc "... O pai da Reba faleceu e isso deixou toda a sua família numa espécie de limbo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:80
translate portuguese act3scene4_0115c38f:

    # pc "Her mother seems to have given up on her own life and Reba has been forced to take care of her."
    pc "A mãe dela parece ter desistido da própria vida e a Reba foi forçada a cuidar dela."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:81
translate portuguese act3scene4_233c26c0:

    # pc "But she's trying her best to move on and be a better version of herself, while also not forgetting about her family."
    pc "Mas ela está a dar o seu melhor para seguir em frente e ser uma versão melhor de si mesma, sem esquecer a família."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:85
translate portuguese act3scene4_b0752170:

    # pc "... Dana lost what she thought her life was going to be."
    pc "... A Dana perdeu o que pensava que a sua vida iria ser."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:86
translate portuguese act3scene4_4054bf2c:

    # pc "The man that was supposed to love her treated her badly and her family didn't support her."
    pc "O homem que era suposto amá-la tratou-a mal e a sua família não a apoiou."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:87
translate portuguese act3scene4_e1dbd7a3:

    # pc "But she's finding herself again, and discovering that there's a lot of love out there if you let yourself be open to it."
    pc "Mas ela está a reencontrar-se e a descobrir que há muito amor por aí, se nos abrirmos a ele."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:91
translate portuguese act3scene4_684ddcd7:

    # pc "... Adrian embraced her true self and some of the people she loved didn't support her."
    pc "... A Adrian abraçou o seu verdadeiro eu e algumas das pessoas que ela amava não a apoiaram."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:92
translate portuguese act3scene4_0baf3bdf:

    # pc "She lost her father because he loved {i}his{/i} idea of who she was more than her actual self."
    pc "Ela perdeu o pai porque ele amava {i}a sua{/i} ideia de quem ela era mais do que o seu verdadeiro eu."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:93
translate portuguese act3scene4_0778a7bc:

    # pc "But she's happier than she's ever been and finding people who love her for who she really is."
    pc "Mas ela está mais feliz do que nunca e a encontrar pessoas que a amam pelo que ela realmente é."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:97
translate portuguese act3scene4_9eadd263:

    # pc "... Kendra is sick and will likely not live to be very old."
    pc "... A Kendra está doente e provavelmente não viverá até uma idade avançada."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:98
translate portuguese act3scene4_5cec7ee5:

    # pc "When she dies, she will lose everybody and everybody will lose her."
    pc "Quando ela morrer, perderá toda a gente e toda a gente perderá ela."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:99
translate portuguese act3scene4_fa1731ad:

    # pc "But she's determined to still love as hard as she can and enjoy life as much as she can while she's alive."
    pc "Mas ela está determinada a continuar a amar com toda a força que puder e a aproveitar a vida o máximo que puder enquanto estiver viva."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:103
translate portuguese act3scene4_a64c27f0:

    # pc "... Juliana lost both of her parents and has grown up with her grandmother."
    pc "... Juliana perdeu ambos os pais e cresceu com a avó."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:104
translate portuguese act3scene4_1653b6af:

    # pc "She's had a hard time making friends and has a lot of fear about loving someone and losing them."
    pc "Tem tido dificuldade em fazer amigos e tem muito medo de amar alguém e de o perder."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:105
translate portuguese act3scene4_3e7f244a:

    # pc "But she's learning to put herself out there anyways, to make herself vulnerable."
    pc "Mas está a aprender a abrir-se na mesma, a tornar-se vulnerável."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:106
translate portuguese act3scene4_57cb2c2d:

    # pc "Because the rewards are worth it."
    pc "Porque as recompensas valem a pena."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:110
translate portuguese act3scene4_6fd90af8:

    # pc "... Mi-Cha hasn't lost anything yet, but she knows she will."
    pc "... Mi-Cha ainda não perdeu nada, mas sabe que vai perder."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:111
translate portuguese act3scene4_c726ce2f:

    # pc "She came to a place, gave her heart to somebody, and now she's being forced to leave that place and her love behind."
    pc "Chegou a um lugar, entregou o seu coração a alguém e agora está a ser forçada a deixar esse lugar e o seu amor para trás."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:112
translate portuguese act3scene4_3d2ddad3:

    # pc "Maybe it'll work out, but in the end. She knows it's better to love and lose than never love at all."
    pc "Talvez tudo corra bem, mas no final... Ela sabe que é melhor amar e perder do que nunca amar."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:119
translate portuguese act3scene4_322b87f1:

    # pc "... Mari has lost everything. Her whole family taken from her in a moment."
    pc "... Mari perdeu tudo. Toda a sua família lhe foi tirada num instante."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:120
translate portuguese act3scene4_29625c9a:

    # pc "She still lives in the shadow of that tragedy, but she shines brightly anyways."
    pc "Ela ainda vive à sombra dessa tragédia, mas brilha intensamente na mesma."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:121
translate portuguese act3scene4_6a46eb5e:

    # pc "She carries on with their love inside of her, knowing that they would be proud of her."
    pc "Ela segue em frente com o amor deles dentro de si, sabendo que eles se orgulhariam dela."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:125
translate portuguese act3scene4_62feec4d:

    # pc "... Izzy lost both of her parents and has been put into a position where she has to care for her two little brothers."
    pc "... A Izzy perdeu os dois pais e foi colocada numa situação em que tem de cuidar dos seus dois irmãos mais novos."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:126
translate portuguese act3scene4_e5564799:

    # pc "She could be resentful of this, but she loves those two boys so much."
    pc "Ela poderia ficar ressentida com isso, mas ama tanto aqueles dois rapazes."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:127
translate portuguese act3scene4_289024f9:

    # pc "When she thought she lost them, she fought so hard to get them back."
    pc "Quando pensou que os tinha perdido, lutou com todas as suas forças para os ter de volta."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:131
translate portuguese act3scene4_a06ddb36:

    # pc "... Jamie loved a boy so much, but he tossed her aside without a word."
    pc "... A Jamie amava tanto um rapaz, mas ele deixou-a de lado sem dizer uma palavra."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:132
translate portuguese act3scene4_9714d5b1:

    # pc "But she kept moving forward, just being herself."
    pc "Mas ela continuou a seguir em frente, sendo apenas ela própria."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:133
translate portuguese act3scene4_7f79356e:

    # pc "And eventually, things came back around and worked out for her."
    pc "E, eventualmente, as coisas deram a volta e correram bem para ela."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:137
translate portuguese act3scene4_d7d23337:

    # pc "And then there's me..."
    pc "E depois sou eu..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:139
translate portuguese act3scene4_6cc0d265:

    # pc "Well, I can only talk about myself..."
    pc "Bem, só posso falar de mim..."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:140
translate portuguese act3scene4_cdb25042:

    # pc "I lost my mom when I was a teenager and it was really hard on me."
    pc "Perdi a minha mãe quando era adolescente e foi muito difícil para mim."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:141
translate portuguese act3scene4_739643a0:

    # pc "I took it out on the people around me and did things I regret."
    pc "Descarreguei nas pessoas à minha volta e fiz coisas das quais me arrependo."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:142
translate portuguese act3scene4_ac0e651a:

    # pc "But I've done my best to change that and make things right."
    pc "Mas fiz o meu melhor para mudar isso e corrigir as coisas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:145
translate portuguese act3scene4_e7e67352:

    # sp "I suppose that's what I should do now."
    sp "Acho que é isso que devo fazer agora."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:146
translate portuguese act3scene4_1e770403:

    # pc "I think so."
    pc "Acho que sim."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:147
translate portuguese act3scene4_2610ae2e:

    # sp "I feel so ashamed. How can I face people?"
    sp "Sinto-me tão envergonhada. Como é que vou conseguir encarar as pessoas?"

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:150
translate portuguese act3scene4_5c7a5888:

    # pc "The ones that really matter still love you, Lisa."
    pc "Aqueles que realmente importam ainda te amam, Lisa."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:151
translate portuguese act3scene4_34903c2d:

    # pc "They feel the same loss that you feel."
    pc "Eles sentem a mesma perda que tu sentes."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:152
translate portuguese act3scene4_a346789c:

    # pc "But they feel like they lost {i}you{/i} as well."
    pc "Mas sentem que também te perderam a ti."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:155
translate portuguese act3scene4_02541c65:

    # tm "It's true, Your Majesty."
    tm "É verdade, Vossa Majestade."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:156
translate portuguese act3scene4_e56ac275:

    # tm "I miss Suzy so much."
    tm "Tenho tantas saudades da Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:157
translate portuguese act3scene4_2b1387cd:

    # tm "And I miss you too."
    tm "E também tenho saudades de ti."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:160
translate portuguese act3scene4_909876ef:

    # sp "Oh God, I'm so sorry, Tammy. Of course you miss her too."
    sp "Oh Deus, lamento imenso, Tammy. Claro que também tens saudades dela."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:161
translate portuguese act3scene4_ddc42ef4:

    # sp "I'll fix this. I'll make it better."
    sp "Vou resolver isto. Vou melhorar as coisas."

# game/Scenes/Update19/Act3/act3scene4.rpy:165
translate portuguese act3scene4_f8a1c7af:

    # sp "Starting with this."
    sp "Começando por isto."

